Texas Flip and Move - Season 2, Episode 8




The Young Guns Duplex Debacle Brings Down the House

Cody and Suzi decide to share duties redesigning a duplex when he takes one side and she takes on the other. Unfortunately, when Cody tries to demolish the rotted half of the house, it all comes crashing down and the Young Guns end up with a one bed, one bath bungalow.




Original Air Date: 06-Nov-2015
